OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,FBill Gates has told the United States
OL,7,FCongress that meeting Jeffrey Epstein
OL,8,Fwas a 'grave error in judgment' and
OL,9,Fthe convicted paedophile attempted to
OL,10,Fuse information about his personal
OL,11,Flife, including his infidelities, to
OL,12,Fpressure Gates.
OL,14,FThe Microsoft co-founder has been
OL,15,Ffacing questions from lawmakers behind
OL,16,Fclosed doors about his relationship
OL,17,Fwith the disgraced financier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
