OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781121970
OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,FIn an opening statement, Gates said he
OL,7,F"should never have met with Epstein in
OL,8,Fthe first place," but that he "never
OL,9,Fwitnessed nor had any indication that
OL,10,FEpstein was engaged in ongoing
OL,11,Fcriminal conduct".
OL,13,FThe tech billionaire became the latest
OL,14,Fpowerful figure linked to Epstein
OL,15,Fcalled to testify before the House
OL,16,FOversight Committee.
OL,18,FAs Gates arrived at the Capitol, he
OL,19,Fnoted that he was there voluntarily
OL,20,Fand said he hoped his testimony would
OL,21,Fbe useful.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@QO]pD@_OUsD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781121970
OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,F"I hope my testimony is helpful to the
OL,7,Fwork, the important work, of the
OL,8,Fcommittee, to find justice for the
OL,9,Fvictims," he said.
OL,11,FThe committee chairman, Republican
OL,12,FRepresentative James Comer, formally
OL,13,Frequested that Gates testify after he
OL,14,Fappeared multiple times in a trove of
OL,15,Fdocuments released by the Justice
OL,16,FDepartment as part of its Epstein
OL,17,Fprobe.
OL,19,FBefore the interview on Wednesday,
OL,20,FComer told reporters that "no one's
OL,21,Faccusing Bill Gates of any wrongdoing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]|D@[OU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
