CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781121970
OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,FHe added that this is about "the
OL,7,Fsurvivors" of Epstein and his
OL,8,Fconfidant Ghislaine Maxwell. "This is
OL,9,Fabout trying to figure out how the
OL,10,Fgovernment failed", he said.
OL,12,FGates said he was introduced to
OL,13,FEpstein through people involved in his
OL,14,Fprofessional and philanthropic work
OL,15,Fand was drawn in by Epstein's claims
OL,16,Fthat he could help raise billions of
OL,17,Fdollars for global health initiatives.
OL,19,FGates says he ended the relationship
OL,20,Fin 2014 after concluding Epstein could
OL,21,Fnot deliver on those promises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
