PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781121970
OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,FGates added that he never went to
OL,7,FEpstein's island or his other infamous
OL,8,Fproperties.
OL,10,F"I have never victimised anyone. While
OL,11,Fhe may have sought to foster a
OL,12,Fpersonal relationship, I was never
OL,13,Finterested in that and never
OL,14,Freciprocated," Gates said.
