OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781121970
OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,FThe remarks come as lawmakers review
OL,7,Fdocuments detailing Gates'
OL,8,Finteractions with Epstein. Included in
OL,9,Fthe files are calendar entries for
OL,10,Fmeetings between Gates and Epstein,
OL,11,Femail correspondence between the two
OL,12,Fabout philanthropic projects and
OL,13,Fphotos of Gates at events that Epstein
OL,14,Falso attended.
OL,16,FTheir relationship began in 2011,
OL,17,Fthree years after Epstein pleaded
OL,18,Fguilty in Florida to soliciting
OL,19,Fprostitution from a minor, and
OL,20,Fcontinued until at least late 2014,
OL,21,Faccording to the documents.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
