OL,3,CBill Gates says meeting Epstein was a
OL,4,C'grave error in judgement'
OL,6,FGates, who chairs the Gates
OL,7,FFoundation, has not been accused of
OL,8,Fwrongdoing in connection with Epstein
OL,9,Fand has repeatedly denied any
OL,10,Fknowledge of Epstein's abuse of girls.
